No Contact Privacy Policy

Effective Date: Feb 17, 2025

1. Introduction

Welcome to No Contact AI! Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your personal information when you use our app.

By using No Contact AI, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

2. Information We Collect

We collect the following types of information:

2.1 Personal Information

Name (if provided)

Email address (if provided)

Account credentials (if using authentication)

Payment information (for premium features, processed securely by third-party payment providers)

2.2 Usage Data

Mood logs, journal entries, and goal tracking data

AI chat interactions (stored securely for personalized insights)

App activity, including features accessed and time spent in the app

2.3 Device Information

Device type and operating system

IP address

App version and performance diagnostics

3. How We Use Your Information

We use your information to:

Provide and improve No Contact AI

Personalize AI-generated responses

Track your progress and provide insights

Send optional notifications or reminders (if enabled by the user)

Ensure security and prevent unauthorized access

4. How We Protect Your Information

We take security seriously and implement:

End-to-end encryption for sensitive data

Secure cloud storage with restricted access

Regular security audits to identify vulnerabilities

5. Sharing of Information

We do not sell or rent your data. However, we may share data:

With service providers (e.g., cloud storage, AI processing) under strict confidentiality agreements

For legal compliance, if required by law

6. Your Choices & Control

You can:

Access and edit your personal data in the app

Delete journal entries, mood logs, or goals at any time

Request data deletion by contacting [Insert Contact Email]

7. Third-Party Integrations

Our app may integrate with third-party services (e.g., Firebase, AI processing tools). These services have their own privacy policies, which we encourage you to review.

8. Children's Privacy

No Contact AI is not intended for users under 13 years old. We do not knowingly collect data from children.

9. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of significant changes through in-app notifications or email.

10. Contact Us

For questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Plkfsdevelopers@gmail.com
